Name: RoguekiniZ
About the game: As part of the RoguekiniZ team you will make runs into Dolan island to learn its areas and eliminate the Zs. As you level up you will get better weapons, gear, traps, and skills. And when you’re ready, make a final run into the mountain base where it all began. Kill Dr Dolan and put an end to the zombie plague. Key Features Every Run Counts Earn xp, level up, and get sweet loot to help you on your next run. You’ll need it because each run consists of multiple stages with challenging, varied mission types like defense, survival, elimination and more. Weapons Use guns, traps, and skills to defeat the zombie hordes. Guns are great but you’ll need to use traps and skills like “Air Strike” to make it through a run. Gear Change your character's outfits with looted gear which also provide stat bonuses. Look good, kill good. Classes Three character classes with specific bonuses to fit multiple play styles. The Soldier specializes in using guns. The Nurse has the best survivability. The Technician gets the most out of traps. Enemies Fight multiple zombie classes from simple shufflers and sprinters to more exotic types that will challenge you in surprising ways. Flexible Challenge The game is meant to test your skills but we have difficulty settings to appeal to players of all levels. Dancing Yes. You Can Dance
